| `app/src/server/chat/tools/invoke-pm-agent.ts` | Chat tool for invoking PM | `createInvokePmAgentTool()` |
| `app/src/server/chat/tools/index.ts` | Chat agent tool factory | `createChatAgentTools()`, `ChatAgentToolDeps` |
| `app/src/server/chat/tools/types.ts` | Tool dependency types | `ChatToolDeps`, `ChatAgentToolDeps`, `ChatToolExecutionContext` |
| `app/src/server/chat/handler.ts` | Chat agent runner | `runChatAgent()` |
| `app/src/server/chat/context.ts` | Chat context + system prompt | `buildSystemPrompt()` (includes PM rendering instructions) |
| `app/src/server/chat/chat-processor.ts` | Message processor | `processChatMessage()` |
